===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|s=带|alt=帯}}
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*s-daːj||waist; belt; zone; flat expanse}}. Cognate with {{cog|bo|སྡེ||part; portion; district}} and {{cog|tbq-lob-pro|*N-day³|t=level expanse; plain}}. Also compare the phonologically similar {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*s-taj||naval; abdomen; center; self}}.

The internet slang usage in lieu of {{l|zh|大}} is a written rendering of internet streamer {{lw|en|Sun Xiaochuan}}'s Sichuan-influenced Standard Mandarin ({{lw|zh|四川普通话}}) accent.

{{rfe|zh|Any relation to, or influence from, {{m|zh|戴}} regarding the homophonic "to wear; to attach to the body" senses?}}

